=======================================================================
 INSTALL
 =======================================================================

 1. cd build
 2. cmake .. -DBUILD_SHARED_LIBS=ON -DCMAKE_BUILD_TYPE=Release

 parameters
    - BUILD_SHARED_LIBS (ON|OFF)
    - CMAKE_BUILD_TYPE (Debug|Release)
    - CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX (/usr/local)

3. make
4. make test
5. make install

